The paper focuses on developing a deep learning approach for image analysis in the field of cell biology and drug screening, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE) sub-categories. The use of multiple instance learning (MIL) and the development of a new MIL operator also suggest relevance to information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
